   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Brazilian Red Cross Flood Response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Brazilian Red Cross and its network are on the front lines of providing emergency relief and aid to all flood-impacted communities in the Brazilian states of Bahia and Minas Gerais. We are providing water, food, hygiene and first aid kits, and other emergency supplies. Many people affected by the flooding will depend on our emergency relief for days and weeks. Many have lost all their possessions and need access to basic supplies.</narrative>
  </description>
